  drop_na(domgross_2013) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = budget_2013,

Lets use our own colours!!!

Segment chart

dinosaurs <- tribble(
  ~period, ~start, ~end,  
  "Triassic Period", -251e6, -225e6,  
  "Late Triassic Period", -225e6, -200e6,  
  "Jurassic Period", -200e6, -150e6,  
  "Late Jurassic Period", -150e6, -145e6)
dinosaurs
## # A tibble: 4  3
##   period                    start        end
##   <chr>                     <dbl>      <dbl>
## 1 Triassic Period      -251000000 -225000000
## 2 Late Triassic Period -225000000 -200000000
## 3 Jurassic Period      -200000000 -150000000
## 4 Late Jurassic Period -150000000 -145000000
dinosaurs %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(y = period,
      yend = period,
      x = start,
      xend = end) +
  geom_segment(size = 5,
               colour = "darkolivegreen")

msleep

Change Some meat to red and No meat to green

msleep %>% 
  count(vore) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = n,
      y = vore) +
  geom_col(aes(fill = ifelse(vore == "herbi", "No Meat", "Some meat"))) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("Some meat" = "red", "No Meat" = "darkolivegreen"),
                    name = "")

count order

msleep %>% 
  count(vore) %>% 
  mutate(vore = fct_reorder(vore, n),
         vore = fct_explicit_na(vore, "Unknown diet")) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = n,
      y = vore) +
  geom_col(aes(fill = ifelse(vore == "herbi", "No Meat", "Some meat"))) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("Some meat" = "red", "No Meat" = "darkolivegreen"),
                    name = "")

canonical order

order_vore <- c("carni", "omni", "insecti", "herbi")

msleep %>% 
  count(vore) %>% 
  mutate(vore = fct_relevel(vore, order_vore),
         vore = fct_explicit_na(vore, "Unknown diet"),
         vore = fct_relevel(vore, "Unknown diet", after = 0)) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = n,
      y = vore) +
  geom_col(aes(fill = ifelse(vore == "herbi", "No Meat", "Some meat"))) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("Some meat" = "red", "No Meat" = "darkolivegreen"),
                    name = "")
